{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the simplified checkout flow with the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/sessions"},{"text":" endpoint does not work for you, or you prefer to have more control over the whole flow, please refer to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"AdvancedFlow.md","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Setting up the Drop-in","level":2,"anchor":"Setting-up-the-Drop-in"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All Components need an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenContext","isActive":true},{"text":". An instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenContext","isActive":true},{"text":" wraps your client key, environment, payment, analytics configuration and so on.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Please read more ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.adyen.com\/development-resources\/client-side-authentication"},{"type":"text","text":" about the client key and how to get one."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Environment.test"},{"type":"text","text":" during testing. When you’re ready to accept live payments, change the value to one of our "},{"overridingTitle":"live environments","type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/Environment","isActive":true,"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"live environments"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We recommend creating a new context for each payment attempt."}]},{"code":["var context: AdyenContext {","    let apiContext = try! APIContext(environment: componentsEnvironment, clientKey: clientKey)","    return AdyenContext(apiContext: apiContext,","                        payment: payment,","                        analyticsConfiguration: analyticsConfiguration)","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create an instance of "},{"code":"AdyenSession.Configuration","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with the response you received from the "},{"code":"\/sessions","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" call and the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenContext","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let configuration = AdyenSession.Configuration(sessionIdentifier: response.sessionId,","                                               initialSessionData: response.sessionData,","                                               context: context)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Call the static ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"initialize"},{"text":" function of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenSession"},{"text":" by providing the configuration and the delegates, which will asynchronously create and return the session instance.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["AdyenSession.initialize(with: configuration, delegate: self, presentationDelegate: self) { [weak self] result in","    switch result {","    case let .success(session):","        \/\/ store the session object","        self?.session = session","    case let .failure(error):","        \/\/ handle the error","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Create a configuration object for ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/DropInComponent","isActive":true},{"text":". Check specific payment method pages to confirm if you need to include additional required parameters.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Check specific payment method pages to confirm if you need to configure additional required parameters.","let dropInConfiguration = DropInComponent.Configuration()","let component = DropInComponent(paymentMethods: paymentMethods,","                                context: context,","                                configuration: dropInConfiguration)",""]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Some payment methods need additional configuration. For example ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/ApplePayComponent","type":"reference"},{"text":". These payment method specific configuration parameters can be set in an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"DropInComponent.Configuration"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"code":["let summaryItems = [","                      PKPaymentSummaryItem(label: \"Item A\", amount: 75, type: .final),","                      PKPaymentSummaryItem(label: \"Item B\", amount: 25, type: .final),","                      PKPaymentSummaryItem(label: \"My Company\", amount: 100, type: .final)","                   ]","let applePayment = try ApplePayPayment(countryCode: \"US\",","                                       currencyCode: \"USD\",","                                       summaryItems: summaryItems)","","let dropInConfiguration = DropInComponent.Configuration()","dropInConfiguration.applePay = .init(payment: applePayment,","                               merchantIdentifier: \"merchant.com.adyen.MY_MERCHANT_ID\")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Also for voucher payment methods like Doku variants, in order for the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/DokuComponent","type":"reference"},{"text":" to enable the shopper to save the voucher