ough its delegate, ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenSessionDelegate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". To handle the results of the Drop-in, the following methods of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenSessionDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" should be implemented:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func didComplete(with result: AdyenSessionResult, component: Component, session: AdyenSession)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method will be invoked when the component finishes without any further steps needed by the application. The application just needs to dismiss the current component, ideally after calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"finalizeIfNeeded"},{"text":" on the component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func didFail(with error: Error, from component: Component, session: AdyenSession)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method is invoked when an error occurred during the use of the Drop-in or the components.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"You can then call the ","type":"text"},{"code":"finalizeIfNeeded","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on the component, dismiss the component’s view controller in the completion callback and display an error message.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func didOpenExternalApplication(component: DropInComponent)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This optional method is invoked after a redirect to an external application has occurred."}]},{"anchor":"Handling-an-action","level":2,"text":"Handling an action","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Actions are handled by the Drop-in via its delegate "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/AdyenSession","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Receiving-redirect","text":"Receiving redirect"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In case the customer is redirected to an external URL or App, make sure to let the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/RedirectComponent","type":"reference"},{"text":" know when the user returns to your app. Do this by implementing the following in your ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIApplicationDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["func application(_ app: UIApplication, open url: URL, options: [UIApplicationOpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","    RedirectComponent.applicationDidOpen(from: url)","    return true","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Drop-in handles the presentation of available payment methods and the subsequent entry of a customer’s payment details. It is initialized with the payment methods of the "},{"code":"\/sessions","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" response, and handles the entire checkout flow under the hood for most of use cases."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/adyen\/dropin"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen\/DropIn"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"DropIn","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Adyen"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Adyen\/documentation\/Adyen"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"doc://Adyen/documentation/Adyen/ApplePayComponent":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A component that handles Apple Pay payments.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/adyen\/applepaycomponent","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Ap